             were indicted for <rs id="t18190526-112-off617" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190526-112-off617" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190526-112-off617" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190526-112-cd618" type="crimeDate">17th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190526-112-off617 t18190526-112-cd618"></join>, 52 lbs. of lead, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190526-112-victim1010" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin George 
                           Hodges
                        <interp inst="t18190526-112-victim1010" type="surname" value="Hodges"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18190526-112-victim1010" type="given" value="Benjamin George"></interp>
