                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190526-112-defend1006 t18190526-112-punish621"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ROWLEY - <rs id="t18190526-112-verdict622" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190526-112-verdict622" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
